Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:24.75,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The culture festival \Nwill finally begin tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:32.01,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I once had someone precious \Nthat I wished to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:06.98,sign_2925_4_Maids__Ghosts___,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Maids, Ghosts, \Nand the Stage of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:06.98,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The culture festival starts \Nfor real tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.81,sign_3045_6_Fujimiya_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimiya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.81,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in a mad rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:13.69,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Some students are prioritizing their \Nclub projects for the festival, like us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:17.07,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,and others are focusing mainly \Non their class projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:22.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nwhat was our class going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,We decided that in homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:25.58,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:30.83,sign_3491_14_Acting_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Acting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:30.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I haven't had room in my head \Nfor anything but acting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:35.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, lately you've been working\Nday and night, as if your life depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, I must admit I'm \Nimpressed by how focused you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,To the point you haven't noticed {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.47,sign_3818_19_Acting_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Acting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:48.23,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.10,sign_4034_22_Haunted_House,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,100)}Haunted House
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.61,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this something you \Nwanted to try, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, I didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If you're aiming to be a stage actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.78,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to be able to play any role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd freeze in front of everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and turn into a scarecrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.10,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That could work, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:16.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:22.13,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your class is doing a haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What's your class doing, Mayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.19,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A maid outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.87,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.88,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Which means?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's dressed like usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you're \Nin the going home club?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:44.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be working at Hitotose's \Ncoffee shop during the festival, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.16,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.22,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing a maid outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.66,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm obviously a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.26,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a maid café!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:56.04,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's doing what \Nshe always does, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:59.30,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Why don't you guys get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the maid café \Npart is true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.09,sign_5738_52_Maid_Caf___,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Maid Café
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.05,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there are \Nlots more Mayu-chans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,All of their costumes \Nwere made based on mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! We have to hurry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Almost got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.20,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.95,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:32.45,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,There! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.75,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You look beautiful, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.44,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.12,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:44.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you had to help me \Nget dressed, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're busy with \Nyour class's café, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.59,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:52.85,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I helped with the other \Ntheater club members' outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to at least help you put yours on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.79,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I truly thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:04.61,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,You've done wonderfully with \Nthe heroine's wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:08.12,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the rest of you \Nshould get changed, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.37,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:17.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Sakuragi Hinako, and I'll be \Nplaying the h-heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:22.38,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakajima Yua, and I'm playing the \Nwealthy young detective who solves the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:27.01,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Natsukawa Kuina, and I'm playing \Nthe caretaker of the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.30,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:32.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi Mayuki-san, \Nwho's playing the mansion's maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:33.89,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:40.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait! I'm not in the play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.15,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't look out of place \Namong the cast at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You should be in it, Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.88,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like I told you, I work behind the scenes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.72,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.79,Main Dialogue Top,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll join us next time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.79,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.49,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,With the costumes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.29,Italics Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone's starting to look \Njust like their characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:03.30,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan really looks like a \Nwealthy young detective, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.80,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd almost think Kuu-chan \Nreally is a caretaker at a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.18,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And the landlady's in her tracksuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tracksuit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.77,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, the landlady is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.29,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Landlady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:22.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I mean... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:25.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai is still in her tracksuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.99,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was a bit surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.02,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.37,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working behind the scenes this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.84,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.70,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:44.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've remained active \Nin the theater club all this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.71,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:50.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I talked to Sensei \Nand decided that we should
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,keep the focus on \Nthe new members this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.54,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.58,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The script I wrote for this production
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.35,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,is better suited to fresh, new performers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You've been working on \Nmemorizing the script, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,How could you not notice \Nwho the other actors were?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:11.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just memorizing my own lines \Nand cues took all of my brain power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:16.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I only just finished memorizing \Nall my lines last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:19.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You do have a lot of lines, \Nbeing the heroine and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:22.75,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I get that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:26.88,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's unbelievable that she didn't \Neven read the other actors' parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.56,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,It is indeed an unusual approach,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.63,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,but it's okay for acting styles \Nto differ from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:38.40,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Some read the whole script and \Ncalculate how they should act within it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:42.64,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,while others focus on mastering \Nonly their own part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.15,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:48.40,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit can be none other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:58.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:02.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't here in the \Ngreat hall at that hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:06.29,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I just reacted naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.76,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.16,Italics Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako-san is truly special.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.35,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.80,Italics Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that her line came to her instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:13.70,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I only just arrived here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.04,Italics Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,proves that she is one with her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:18.82,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,To be stuck in the middle of this incident \Nall of a sudden is truly a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:19.50,Italics Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,My choice to cast her as the heroine \Nwas clearly not a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:23.35,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought this vacation that I was \Nsupposed to enjoy would end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.48,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:31.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, I seriously considered \Nleaving this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.90,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan, don't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:42.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I once had someone precious \Nthat I wished to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.96,Italics Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to do that \Nduring the play, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought an incident \Nlike this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Someone here is the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:56.59,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And this handkerchief is \Nthe greatest evidence of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! It was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:12.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I had someone precious \Nthat I wished to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.12,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:22.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've made it to the end \Nwithout messing up any of my lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.94,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, though you came \Ndangerously close at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.71,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You were great, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.34,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I can't wait until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have done it without all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I made it this far because of you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Your hard work paid off, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.35,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yua-chan, great job—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.96,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The show isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.73,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.99,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.11,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we'll rehearse it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.74,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The show is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.74,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,We have no time for playing around, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:03.84,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.84,sign_14746_175_Fujimiya_Festiva,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Fujimiya Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_184_Tea_Club__Tea_Ro,Poster1,0000,0000,0000,,Tea Club \NTea Room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_185_Science__Club,Poster2,0000,0000,0000,,Science\N Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_186_Experiments_,Poster2,0000,0000,0000,,Experiments:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_187___Color_changing,Poster2,0000,0000,0000,,- Color-changing \Nwater \N- Slime \N- Air cannon \N- Hydroponics \NDisplay \N- Cartesian diver
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_188_Dumplings,Poster3,0000,0000,0000,,Dumplings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_189_Wind__Ensemble_C,Poster4,0000,0000,0000,,Wind\N Ensemble Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_190_Concert,Poster4,0000,0000,0000,,Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_191_Time_Schedule_,Poster4,0000,0000,0000,,Time Schedule:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.51,sign_14890_192_Class_3_E__Movie,Poster5,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3-E \NMovie \NScreening
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.52,sign_14974_193_Performance__Per,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Performance \NPerformance: Handbells \NMovie: "The Day is Long, Walk on Boy" \NChorus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:32.52,sign_14974_193_Performance__Per,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Year 3 | Chorus \NTheater Society | Play: "And Everyone Is Part of the ABC Tragedy Case File!" \NClosing Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:41.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,S-So this is a culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.28,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're too impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.79,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.82,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Mayu-chan and the landlady?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:52.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's class is \Nabout to open their maid café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And Chiaki-senpai said she had \Na meeting with Ruriko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.99,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.55,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted us all to eat these together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,All of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.73,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just buy everything you could carry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:05.18,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:09.43,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This is my own selection of the \Nbest of culture festival gourmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.94,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this grilled chicken skewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:18.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This is made with free-range chicken meat \Nprovided by a local farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.07,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The meat's savory flavor \Nand texture are exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:25.95,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And the flavor of the tamari soy sauce \Nin the glaze is delectable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.21,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And this yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:34.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This was delivered directly from a town \Nthat's famous for its B-grade cuisine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The crispy bean sprouts create \Na perfect balance of textures!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.47,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And just look at this takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It was made by a transfer student \Nstraight from Kansai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:50.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Fluffy on the outside, gooey on the inside...\N it's a true masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.92,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you eat one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.93,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A glorious harmony fills your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:57.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.11,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You keep talking about how they taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Have you eaten all these already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.99,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:09.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all morning conquering \Nevery single food stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.12,sign_17398_226_Seaweed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What? A-All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of stomach do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.21,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.51,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:23.03,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:26.39,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a culture festival if you \Ndon't enjoy the food stall cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:30.26,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there are many \Nother students who've taken it this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from the stalls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.94,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,you also can't miss the cafés \Nand other shops run by the classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like Mayu-chan's maid café!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.36,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I've already checked all of those out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:47.49,sign_18243_242_Maid_Caf___,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Maid Café
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:47.49,sign_18243_243_Recommended__Pan,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Recommended \N{\fs20}Pancake and\N Omelet Rice Combo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:45.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! They have a pancake \Nand omelet rice combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most important item \Non their menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat there next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:55.37,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you two can still eat more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. This is pretty good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:04.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But should we really be spending \Nall our time doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.65,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Our play is in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a while off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:13.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we practiced until \Nreally late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel a little uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real worrywart, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You got all your lines perfect yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have no choice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.83,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we run through \Njust the opening lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.67,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.43,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And who is this young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.47,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.93,sign_19983_268_Personnel__Only_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Personnel \NOnly \NBeyond \NThis Point
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.93,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could you forget the first scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.76,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,We practiced that part over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.72,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, after practice ended yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:09.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to check out \Neveryone else's parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.56,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Someone here is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.70,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:16.65,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Reading all those lines \Nmade you forget your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.71,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.46,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.33,sign_3818_19_Acting_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Acting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You read something new \Nand forgot the old stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:24.46,sign_20652_282_Everyone_Else_s_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Everyone Else's Lines
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Is your brain a noodle press or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.25,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:31.47,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a food stall with \Nreally good tokoroten noodles...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.94,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.11,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm gonna be so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.37,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting nervous after all we've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.77,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:15:00.00,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No, I'm not the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just practiced again earlier, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.00,Flashback Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}All wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.63,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have Yua-sama to \Nback you up on the stage, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,so all you need to do \Nis act with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll support you as much as I can, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.27,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.26,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And who is this young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:21.33,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... I feel like the mother \Nof a child who's a real handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:28.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought an incident \Nlike this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.22,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako's acting has gotten much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Someone here is the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:39.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And this handkerchief is \Nthe greatest evidence of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.63,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I was so distracted by Hinako,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.44,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.34,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where is this handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have a handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the lady has misplaced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.21,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is the handkerchief you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you, Miss Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.98,Main Dialogue,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return it after the play, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:38.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the handkerchief you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:54.38,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this handkerchief is \Nthe greatest evidence of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.02,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:18:00.69,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of the perfume on this \Nhandkerchief tells us who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they managed \Nto get back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,If it came to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:04.27,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to ad-lib \Nrunning out there to take it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.41,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone recognize this scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.27,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, you'd ruin the play's setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:15.28,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing everyone acting on a stage \Nmakes them seem like different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.24,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The colorful spotlights,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.66,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,the gorgeous costumes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.16,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,the speech patterns \Nthey don't normally use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.91,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,They all look like they're having fun, \Nand they're shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.42,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And to think that I'm speaking \Nin front of all these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.51,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a different person, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:37.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,In the short time \Nsince I came to this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:40.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,many people have passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:47.51,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But there is still something truly \Nprecious that I wish to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:47.51,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew it'd be so fun \Nto speak in front of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:50.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that something is within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:02.01,Main Dialogue,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes all of today's performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.74,Main Dialogue,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:16.98,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's like what happened earlier \Nwas just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:17.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.60,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I acted so stuck-up toward you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then I messed up myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,All's well that ends well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.35,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go \Nto the after-party together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.92,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you're so cute when \Nyou're being honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?! I'm always cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.63,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako-san, Yua-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.64,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Your acting was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.14,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:09.55,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I ruined the script you wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:12.89,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes accidents are a necessary spice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.93,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,That was the kind of wonderful ad-lib \Nyou can only see on a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.52,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I was deeply moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.88,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, if this \Nproduction was successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:26.34,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I had planned to formally start up \Nthe theater club again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:27.38,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.16,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.54,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The theater club will have \Nits new start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.14,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, Hinako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.54,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to make \Nyour show business debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.08,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.84,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's star on TV together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's far too aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She can't, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:52.31,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan will be working hard \Nwith Hitotose from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.92,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's a theater troupe we started \Nwith our apartment's tenants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:03.32,Main Dialogue,Text,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:02.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't put on a \Nperformance yet, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.32,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.68,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:10.85,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Supporting club members in their \Nactivities is part of an advisor's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It scares me to think of \NHinako as the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for worrying about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never said I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.72,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:26.72,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,The after-party is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.35,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Now that our troupe has grown,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.73,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,let's do our best to make it to Suzuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:39.98,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried when I first came to Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:44.61,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe I've gotten just \Na little closer to who I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.61,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:50.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:36.43,sign_33687_411_The_Lost_Swimsui,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,6390)}The Lost Swimsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:31.17,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,My choice to cast Hinako-san \Nas the heroine was not a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.40,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,For our next performance, \Nhow about a show in summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:37.20,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,taking place at the beach, \Nand starring girls in swimsuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:39.27,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Lost Swimsuit."
